    ''' <summary>
    ''' Cause: (0:130 - (0:136
    ''' <para>
    ''' Conditions: (1:130) - (1:131)
    ''' </para>
    ''' <para>
    ''' Effect: (5:130) - (5:139)
    ''' </para>
    ''' <para>
    ''' Furcadia Dice Role handler
